On this edition of Star Wars: Return Of The Trendi Jack and Miles discuss the potential Executive Order to relieve $50k in student debt nationwide, Ryan Reynolds and Rob McElhenney have invested in a Football Club, Ellen "crushed" her People's Choice Awards speech, and Chris Paul is joining the Suns!
